<ab facs="#facs_370_r1l21">vvircʒburgers <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> wegen . Als etlich <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_370_r1l22">kacʒenElmbogen diener . <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> gefangen <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_370_r1l23">gar gnediklıch <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> vnd <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat / Alſo <expan>vven<ex>n</ex></expan> ewr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_370_r1l24"><expan>durchl<ex>euhtikeit</ex></expan> hinab an den Rein kum . ſey <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ymand<ex>en</ex></expan> der ewr </ab>
